# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:40
msgid "Project"
msgstr "Proyek"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:40
msgid ""
"A **project** includes references to all the video files and edits "
"(animations, titles, etc...), saved in a single file."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah **proyek** mencakup referensi ke semua file video dan suntingan "
"(animasi, judul, dll...), yang disimpan dalam satu file."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:41
msgid "Timeline"
msgstr "Garis Waktu"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:41
msgid ""
"The **timeline** is an editing user interface that represents edits and "
"clips on a horizontal ruler. Time progresses from left to right."
msgstr ""
"**Garis waktu** adalah antarmuka pengguna pengeditan yang merepresentasikan "
"suntingan dan klip pada penggaris horizontal. Waktu berjalan dari kiri ke "
"kanan."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:42
msgid "Track"
msgstr "Jalur"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:42
msgid ""
"A separate **layer** on the timeline, which can hold clips. A timeline is "
"made up of many tracks, stacked vertically."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah **lapisan** terpisah pada garis waktu, yang dapat menampung klip. "
"Garis waktu terdiri dari banyak jalur yang ditumpuk secara vertikal."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:43
msgid "Clip"
msgstr "Klip"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:43
msgid ""
"A **trimmed** portion of video, audio, or both positioned on a track, and at "
"a specific position in time. When files are dropped on the timeline, they "
"are represented as a Clip."
msgstr ""
"Bagian **terpotong** dari video, audio, atau keduanya yang ditempatkan pada "
"jalur, dan pada posisi waktu tertentu. Ketika file dijatuhkan ke garis "
"waktu, mereka direpresentasikan sebagai Klip."

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:44
msgid "Transition"
msgstr "Transisi"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../quick_tutorial.rst:44
msgid ""
"A method to **blend** two images. Transitions can take many forms, including "
"cuts, dissolves, and wipes."
msgstr ""
"Metode untuk **menggabungkan** dua gambar. Transisi dapat berbentuk berbagai "
"macam, termasuk potongan, larut, dan sapuan."

